579
01:05:19,015 --> 01:05:21,575
It's hard to get started.

580
01:05:23,486 --> 01:05:24,748
It's Duvallier's dog.

581
01:05:24,954 --> 01:05:27,582
- It'll bite you.
- He doesn't bite.

582
01:05:32,261 --> 01:05:34,161
En garde, Easter Bonnet.

583
01:05:35,731 --> 01:05:38,291
Help me, you guys!
Get the heretic!

584
