You're really getting on my nerves.

585
01:05:44,040 --> 01:05:46,065
Go, Julien!

586
01:05:52,682 --> 01:05:55,082
Julien, have you gone mad!

587
01:05:57,119 --> 01:05:59,019
Your best suit.

588
01:05:59,755 --> 01:06:02,155
