01:19:12,280 --> 01:19:13,907
It's no fun, let me tell you.

720
01:19:18,386 --> 01:19:20,217
Try it. Don't be scared.

721
01:19:21,456 --> 01:19:23,754
Go on. Keep your head up.

722
01:19:27,362 --> 01:19:28,727
Get back up.

723
01:19:29,097 --> 01:19:32,032
- Bed wetter.
